2. 格式与字段

* `*_clean_lineages.tsv`：`sample_token`, `replicate`, `marker`, `taxon_rank`, `taxon_name`, `raw_read_count`, `clean_read_count`, `confidence`, `retained_flag`
* `negative_subtraction_log.tsv`：`sample_token`, `replicate`, `marker`, `taxon_rank`, `taxon_name`, `raw_read_count`, `control_ceiling`, `clean_read_count`
* `low_abundance_filter_log.tsv`：`sample_token`, `replicate`, `marker`, `taxon_rank`, `taxon_name`, `reason`
* `replicate_consistency_log.tsv`：`sample_token`, `marker`, `taxon_rank`, `taxon_name`, `replicate_support_n`, `retained_flag`
